        <updateDate>2021-04-30T15:22:53Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine in the Courtroom Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a framework to allow federal court proceedings&#8212;in district courts, in circuit courts, and at the Supreme Court&#8212;to be photographed, recorded, broadcast, or televised. Specifically, it authorizes the presiding judge to permit media coverage of court proceedings, subject to requirements and limitations. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
